Interface NodeObserver<OUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    OUT - The type of the output received from a OutputNode.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NodeObserverAdapter

    public interface NodeObserver<OUT>
    NodeObserver defines an observer interface for receiving callbacks from an OutputNode.
